autonomous_agent_apis.name: SuperAGI
autonomous_agent_apis.description: SuperAGI is an open-source autonomous AI agent framework that enables developers to build, manage, and run useful autonomous agents quickly and reliably. It supports customization and integration with various tools.

autonomous_agent_apis.name: MS-Agent
autonomous_agent_apis.description: MS-Agent is a lightweight framework designed to empower agents with autonomous exploration capabilities. It provides a flexible and extensible architecture for building intelligent agents.

autonomous_agent_apis.name: OpenAgentsControl
autonomous_agent_apis.description: OpenAgentsControl is an AI agent framework for plan-first development workflows with approval-based execution. It supports multi-language development including TypeScript, Python, and Go.

autonomous_agent_apis.name: Autonomys Agents
autonomous_agent_apis.description: Autonomys Agents is an experimental framework for building AI agents that can interact with social networks and other platforms. It supports extensibility for different agent types.

autonomous_agent_apis.name: The Definitive and Unified AI Agents Framework
autonomous_agent_apis.description: A comprehensive and modular framework designed to automate anything and everything using state-of-the-art AI agent techniques.

autonomous_agent_apis.name: AutoAgent
autonomous_agent_apis.description: AutoAgent provides a common interface for asynchronous running, debugging, and deployment of autonomous agents, with resources and quickstart guides.
